headline: Autodesk (ADSK) Valuation Check After Recent Share Price Weakness
summary: Autodesk (ADSK) has been drawing attention after a period of weaker share performance, with the stock showing negative returns over the past week, month and past 3 months. That backdrop raises new questions about its current valuation. See our latest analysis for Autodesk. The recent weak 7 day and 90 day share price returns sit alongside a year to date share price return of a 3.54% decline. headline: 3 S&P 500 Stocks We Approach with Caution
summary: The S&P 500 (^GSPC) is often seen as a benchmark for strong businesses, but that doesn’t mean every stock is worth owning. Some companies face significant challenges, whether it’s stagnating growth, heavy debt, or disruptive new competitors.
